name: Anubis
description:
#MaskSeries : Anubis

In ancient vedic tradition, Yamaraja, the God of Death is accompanied by Dogs and he himself has appeared as a Dog to join the Pandavas in their final days towards Amarnath shrine, eventually guiding Yudhisthira into heaven.

In Nepal, which is a hindu country, people to offer blessings to dogs which are regarded as messengers of Yamaraj, the god of death and underworld (hell).

===
